" />？"},{"pid":"6b61b1f8d0e210f52c2e920a6f414d30bea8d262","tid":2387994,"uid":258345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T21:45:40.000Z","msg":"respect"},{"pid":"55a497a7fec5ca108c563532b1cf571a4d2bd85e","tid":2387994,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T22:20:18.000Z","msg":"新官上任三把火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留名跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c3f2902b8e5ae9a03703d0378055afcd878396","tid":2387994,"uid":13503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"66176eef85cfa03b852ad2ec0e28463173038dc7","tid":2387994,"uid":112581,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:48:25.000Z","msg":"笑左 到今日個post仲用咁多人OMDB<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢講到班法官冇責任個一刻已經知道又要玩體制嘴炮抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T22:23:28.000Z","msg":"OMDB俾人O完就失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751c3c9f4c279f06b06741a284fee2813c57566b","tid":2387994,"uid":121721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T22:28:39.000Z","msg":"同北京尋求共識？咪玩啦，黨治就係法治，習主席的話就係真理。<br />\n<br />\n想玩petition politics都要朝庭肯俾你玩先得㗎"},{"pid":"2d51b775aab3e96ce743337bbcdb82073c12dec4","tid":2387994,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T22:43:01.000Z","msg":"等睇文匯大公頭條返擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a972fd6f787fd62d6b29419846eedb56ab70f0","tid":2387994,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T23:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee637ceefc6d27358277760f640cc169809bb69d","tid":2387994,"uid":142763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90f990f6f968c86cb9ed3a0262349b707b0720f1","tid":2387994,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T18:11:02.000Z","msg":"資深大律師夏博義本月21日由另一資深大律師戴啟思手上，接過象徵大律師公會主席身份的小木椅，物輕責任重，即使遭受中方宣傳機器狙擊，他仍依心直說，批評「港版國安法」讓部份國安人員超然於法律之上，破壞法治，這位以同樣力度譴責暴力示威行為的新任主席自言是中間派，但強調法治是要當權者受約束，並直言北京要法官與政府合作是走錯方向，堅持爭取與北京破冰，尋求修改《國安法》，即使撞牆都要一試。<br />\n<br />\n記者 梁穎妍<br />\n<br />\n1993年來港執業的夏博義，多年來英港兩邊跑，他接受《蘋果》專訪時表示，從未想過要將自己置身這個位置，笑言對人們希望再有非華人擔任主席感驚訝，也擔心工作量太多；直至去年12月有資深公會成員邀請他出選主席，他認同刻下香港需要對憲法、人權法有認識的人擔任主席，故被說服參選，「這些題目很敏感，不同面向都有人持強烈意見」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210131/FKETP7FOOBCI3E2533NOXX5QMM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210131%2FFKETP7FOOBCI3E2533NOXX5QMM%2F&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=39f4f8d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210131%2FFKETP7FOOBCI3E2533NOXX5QMM%2F&h=29d3fdab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210131/FKETP7FOOBCI3E2533NOXX5QMM/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T23:14:54.000Z","msg":"睇嚟條友唔使好耐就入大坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bff1a7368e99217f06684175c9e2a37894b4b7c","tid":2387994,"uid":121937,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T23:19:48.000Z","msg":"佢講既野只係正常人會講既說話<br />\n班建制派成日話要司法改革，根本第一個要整頓就係警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔係唔知，佢地係扮唔知姐"},{"pid":"5ebf74c7a3b8bbcf0f273298565fa51ae23db10f","tid":2387994,"uid":93519,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T23:45:35.000Z","msg":"根本夏博義越高調越安全,正如12港人一樣<br />\n其實中國最驚就係上報,一個面子國家,做D野成日都係為淡氣,柒左又拗底<br />\n正如上次拉領事都係屈人叫雞,搞大左之後好快放番<br />\n而且中共大把生意收埋係英聯邦島國,唔會敢同英國反面"},{"pid":"d1b5b0490e7bf32183212c6b6d4336e3771749f4","tid":2387994,"uid":302165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T00:32:07.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;After the Bill was suspended, when the protest then became violent and entered into the field of not just a passager of disobediance but actual violence. I totally condemn them if you attacked the legislature you are attacking democracy. Some of their demands I think were unrealistic. Total amnesty is unrealistic, you know.<br />\n<br />\nMy impression is that the Department of Justice is much too aggressive in pusuing these cases and I sincerely hope that I can communicate with the SJ on  a range of issues most certainly quite soon I will be seeking meeting with her. <br />\n<br />\nThe law has been damaged more by the National Security Law. But it is not dead, it's damaged and not been killed, it may yet be killed in the future.<br />\n<br />\nIt may be hopeless, I may be met with a complete break wall of refusal to discuss or considered, but I have to try.<br />\n<br />\nI think various leaders of Beijing of on record saying they don't like the idea of independent judge, they want judges to be under government control and carry out government orders. Well, that's not what was agreed for Hong Kong, China forces through a change of that kind, it will be the end of Hong Kong.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"a84445649ac8717afb9ed2971cff1603b69f0465","tid":2387994,"uid":3967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T00:37:22.000Z","msg":"佢又犯國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea619c54a1fe3273cf8938c427cfe7532507d44","tid":2387994,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T00:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}